<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٤٤١ -<span class="c5"> عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِذَا كَبَّرْتَ خَلْفَ الْإِمَامِ عَلَى الْجِنَازَةِ فَأَسْمِعْ نَفْسَكَ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>